<div class="container details">
  <h2>Blood Donation</h2>
  <p class="lead">Please read and agree to the following terms and conditions before proceeding with your blood donation.</p>
  <div class="terms">
    <h3>Terms and Conditions</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>1. You must be at least 18 years old and in good health to donate blood.</li>
      <li>2. Donating blood should not cause harm to your health. If you have any medical conditions or concerns, please consult with a doctor before donating.</li>
      <li>3. You will need to disclose any medication you are taking, as well as recent travel history.</li>
      <li>4. The blood you donate will be used for patients in need of blood transfusions and other medical treatments.</li>
      <li>5. Your personal information will be kept confidential and used only for the purposes of the blood donation program.</li>
      <li>6. By donating blood, you consent to having your blood tested for safety and compatibility.</li>
      <li>7. The blood donation center reserves the right to refuse donation if you do not meet the eligibility criteria.</li>
      <li>8. You agree to follow the guidelines and instructions provided by the staff at the donation center.</li>
      <li>9. You understand that side effects may occur, such as dizziness or lightheadedness, but that they are generally mild and temporary.</li>
      <li>10. By donating blood, you help save lives, and your contribution is highly appreciated.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class="text-center">
    <%= form_with model: @donor_handbook, method: :post do |f| %> 
      <%= f.hidden_field :donor_id, value: params[:donor_id] %> 
      <div class="form-check">
        <%= f.check_box :terms_accepted, required: true, class: "form-check-input" %>
        <%= f.label :terms_accepted, "I agree to the terms and conditions", class: "form-check-label" %>
      </div>
      <div class="submit"><%= f.submit "Submit", class: "btn" %></div>
    <% end %> 
  </div>
</div>

